title: Duo Partners Looking For Ranked Team
body: Me and a mate want to participate in a serious ranked team at least gold+. We are currently in silver but we haven't been bothered to play ranked that much so our rank is low.  I mainly play Jungle and my mate likes to ADC/Mid. Add me in game if you have both spots available (Cosmic Phantom).

replies.body: So your silvers and you expect everyone else to be gold? That's really fair.
I think they wanted a ranked team that is gold.
